RESTful API interface to RVI Local Node.

For IoTivity 
------------
export OCTBSTACK_LIBS="-L$HOME/GeniviDemo/iotivity/out/linux/x86_64/release -loctbstack -Wl,-rpath=$HOME/GeniviDemo/iotivity/out/linux/x86_64/release"
export OCTBSTACK_CFLAGS="-I$HOME/GeniviDemo/iotivity/resource/csdk/stack/include -I$HOME/GeniviDemo/iotivity/resource/c_common -I$HOME/GeniviDemo/iotivity/resource/c_common/ocrandom/include -DTCP_ADAPTER -DROUTING_EP"

Android Build for IoTivity
--------------------------
scons TARGET_OS=android TARGET_ARCH=armeabi-v7a ANDROID_GRADLE=$HOME/android-studio/gradle/gradle-2.8/bin/gradle ANDROID_HOME=$HOME/Android/Sdk ANDROID_NDK=$HOME/android-ndk/

RVI Testing(Remote)
-------------------
ssh -p1066 rvi@rvi-test3.nginfotpdx.net 
scp -P1066 <file> rvi@rvi-test3.nginfotpdx.net:

RVI Repositories
----------------
https://github.com/PDXostc/rvi_core 
https://github.com/PDXostc/rvi_core/tree/master/doc

sudo vi /etc/apt/sources.list
Add 'deb http://packages.erlang-solutions.com/ubuntu trusty contrib'
sudo apt-get update
Key Server Error : sudo apt-key adv --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com --recv-keys HEX
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install esl-erlang python-jsonrpclib

Quick Test
----------
wget -q0 --no-check-certificate https://github.com/PDXostc/rvi_core/releases/download/v0.5.0/rvi_0.5.0-1ubuntu1_amd64.deb
sudo dpkg -i rvi_0.5.0-1ubuntu1_amd64.deb

Register an RVI Service
/usr/lib/rvi_core/rvi_service hello
Result
genivi.org/node/1cb83d66-2b20-449a-a935-b2f030504952/hello

Invoke the service from another terminal
/usr/lib/rvi_core/rvi_call genivi.org/node/1cb83d66-2b20-449a-a935-b2f030504952/hello


Using HTTP
curl -H "Content-Type: application/json" -X POST -d '{"jsonrpc": "2.0","id":"1", "method": "message", "params":{"timeout":1457399092,"service_name": "genivi.org/node/1cb83d66-2b20-449a-a935-b2f030504952/hello","parameters ":{}}}' http://localhost:9001

curl -H "Content-Type: application/json" -X 4,"service_name": "genivi.org/node/1cb83d66-2b20-449a-a935-b2f030504952/hello","parameters":{"a":"b"}}}' http://localhost:9001

{"jsonrpc":"2.0", "id":"1", "method": "message", "params":{"timeout":1459388884,"service_name": "genivi.org/node/1cb83d66-2b20-449a-a935-b2f030504952/hello","parameters":{"a":"b"}}}
{"jsonrpc": "2.0","id":"1", "method": "message", "params":{"timeout":1457399092,"service_name": "genivi.org/node/1cb83d66-2b20-449a-a935-b2f030504952/hello","parameters ":{}}}




